  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nAnvil\r\n\r\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\r\n\r\n- [X] Foundry\r\n- [X] Foundryup\r\n\r\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\r\n\r\nforge 0.2.0 (9add73c 2022-10-23T00:09:34.410537162Z)\r\n\r\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\r\n\r\nanvil --fork-url ....\r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nWhen calling the impersonate account it returns a TX hash, but when trying to retrieve the Receipt it returns not found.\r\n\r\nIf I evm_mine after every call after the impersonate call it works as expected.\r\n\r\nAuto mine is enabled ",
